{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, be careful where you step.<CR>The floor falls out sometimes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? Is it like a trap or something!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "No, no, it's just an old tunnel,<CR>so it shows its age in places."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "But a group of us went around restoring it, so I think it should be okay..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Just as long as you didn't bring anything heavy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Heavy... That describes Pana to a T..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x205,
            "name_id": 0x1f,
            "extra_id": 0x216,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Moo?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I wonder... I think this much will be okay."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Pana is a girl, too, so I'm sure she doesn't want to be called heavy, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Right, Pana? Ayesha's so mean, huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x205,
            "name_id": 0x1f,
            "extra_id": 0x216,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oink moo..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, oh, Pana, I'm sorry.<CR>I didn't mean it that way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x205,
            "name_id": 0x1f,
            "extra_id": 0x216,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oink moo!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "This is such a large passage... I wonder how the people of the past made this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Who knows? I'm sure it was a tunnel to transport things, but they must've gone to a lot trouble to make it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "You're right. It's amazing how they just carved out the inside of a rock-hard mountain."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Actually, the materials that're used in this passage themselves would make me good money."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "With just this one pillar alone, I could live work-free for at least five years."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "B-But, you can't! If you took the pillar, wouldn't the passage fall?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. No doubt, it'd fall."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "B-But, then we wouldn't be able to get away safely..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Stop it. I'm not planning on taking this pillar."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I'm just saying that if there is any part I could take away, that'd be it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Let's not do that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x49,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Hehehahaha, hmm. I guess I shouldn't think about striking it rich..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "That's right. Steadily, little by little is the best way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "You're right. I think that's best, too. When you say it, it sounds very persuasive."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "...It's just, aiming to strike it rich is the best thing about being a prospector."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "On second thought, just one pillar<CR>won't... *gulp*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Hyah! Regina, stop! I don't wanna fall!"
        }
    ]
}